WEBVTT

00:06:58.604 --> 00:07:01.134
And you can, too. It's not difficult.

00:07:01.739 --> 00:07:05.643
Before we fill our shopping carts
and our landfills

00:07:05.667 --> 00:07:08.298
with extra items that we don't want,

00:07:08.322 --> 00:07:11.938
let's pause next time
we are shopping online

00:07:11.962 --> 00:07:17.646
and think twice about what we all
hopefully really do want:

00:07:17.670 --> 00:07:20.005
a beautiful Earth to call home.

00:07:20.394 --> 00:07:21.556
Thank you.

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:24.846
(Applause)